  "description": "<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201601/aabc81099e6d4b2a9a0d3374d66c3b27.jpg\" /></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t不知不觉五步法已经到了关键的开写环节，第四部分我们一同来看看在行文时我们需要脑海里具备哪些连接观点的表达呢？</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t在英语写作，尤其是学术性的英语写作中，linking words&nbsp;有着非常不容小觑的作用。</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t在托福综合写作考试中，都需要有这样一群默默连接听力和阅读观点的连接词撑场面。那么究竟有哪些类型的连接词我们可以参考呢&nbsp;跟着Yiyi来瞧一瞧&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t1、Sequence&nbsp;表示顺序</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\tfirst, to begin with, first of all, at first, in the first place, second, third</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\tnext, following this, then, last</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\teventually, in the end, finally, ultimately, in conclusion, in summary, last but no least, to sum up</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\tmeanwhile, at the same time, simultaneously</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t2、Comparing and contrasting&nbsp;&nbsp;类比和对比</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\tin the same way, similarly, similar to, likewise, like, differ from, in comparison, compared with,</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\ton the other hand, in contrast, nonetheless, nevertheless, yet, but, however, however, conversely, on the contrary,&nbsp;but, despite, in spite of, even so, however, whereas, conversely, yet, nevertheless, on the contrary, even though, while, rather than&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t3、Cause and effect</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\towing to, since, because, since, as, for, in that, owing to, due to, contribute to &nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\taccordingly, as a consequence, as a result, consequently, for this reason, hence, in consequence, so, so that, therefore, thus, under these conditions, inevitably</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t4、Generalising</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\tgenerally, in general, as a rule, normally, on the whole, usually, in most cases</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t5、Giving examples</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\tfor example, for instance, such as</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t6、Showing attitude</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\tFortunately, luckily, unfortunately, undoubtedly, admittedly, apparently, obviously, evidently, certainly</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t7、Adding more information</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\tfurthermore, as well as, besides, moreover, apart from this, in addition, nor, not only...but also, too, what's more</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t8、Emphasising</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\tespecially, in particular, particularly, notably, chiefly, in detail, mainly</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 25.2px;\">\n\t<strong>这里为大家推荐几个精品托福课程：</strong></p>\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"line-height: 25.2px; width: 600px;\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 293px;\">\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/course/4432824?ch_source=ipo_en_0_rw&amp;editorid=b2b62c7b\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>新版零基础直达新托福90分</strong></a></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<strong><a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/16263970/demo\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201511/7dec2c33b3364bcab765a6b8ae52323c.gif\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/course/4432824?ch_source=ipo_en_0_rw&amp;editorid=b2b62c7b\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201511/73441fbfae8f47e9a1e24e2024c835bc.jpg\" /></a></strong></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/course/4431339?ch_source=ipo_en_0_rw&amp;editorid=b2b62c7b\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>新版初中水平直达新托福90分</strong></a></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<strong><a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/16275345/demo\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.